Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I never did eat, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure I should be your mother?
